96
00:08:04,810 --> 00:08:07,710
Je to dobrý.

97
00:08:07,710 --> 00:08:09,960
Neumřeš.

98
00:08:11,860 --> 00:08:13,750
No ne,

99
00:08:14,570 --> 00:08:18,050
