105
00:08:39,620 --> 00:08:41,620
Ah, bože.

106
00:08:41,620 --> 00:08:45,630
Vážně. To je můra.

107
00:08:50,980 --> 00:08:52,270
Vodu!

108
00:08:52,270 --> 00:08:56,310
Ugh. Proč se tak chová?

109
00:08:56,310 --> 00:09:00,570
