143
00:10:58,380 --> 00:11:00,580
Proč nemůžu dovnitř?

144
00:11:01,600 --> 00:11:03,240
To je zvláštní...

145
00:11:10,330 --> 00:11:12,630
O co jí jde?

146
00:11:13,610 --> 00:11:16,090
Možná, že je tahle Ahjumma...

147
00:11:16,110 --> 00:11:18,080
špión?

148
00:11:33,490 --> 00:11:35,420
Nam Da Jeong.

149
00:11:36,450 --> 00:11:38,370
