179
00:13:08,190 --> 00:13:10,270
tak je ti doufám jasné, co se stane.

180
00:13:10,270 --> 00:13:10,940
Ano.

181
00:13:10,980 --> 00:13:13,130
Nam Da Jeong.

182
00:13:13,130 --> 00:13:15,300
Promluvme si.

183
00:13:20,380 --> 00:13:22,340
Varuju tě.

184
00:13:22,340 --> 00:13:24,870
